<p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.culture.gouv.fr/documentation/phocem/Albums/Soury-presentation.pdf&amp;sa=U&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiM1N7ZiqrKAhUG-2MKHUyMDP4QFggVMAQ&amp;sig2=VUbiJsm_XlXUIagKoKGmcQ&amp;usg=AFQjCNFSQnt7fT6Hff7UcFA2wyp8ZRFgxw">This pdf describes the collection.</a></p>

